    "causal_summary": "The session-capturing runtime used one broad `qualityValidation.valid` boolean as the last indexing gate. That made it hard to express the intended policy: some failures should abort the write, some should allow a write but skip indexing, and V10-only source-mismatch diagnostics should still be able to write and index when stronger gates pass.",
